  "text": "The expression of six selected differentially expressed genes were determined with qPCR to verify the differential expression observed in the RNAseq analysis. Oligonucleotide primers (Table S1 ) were designed using the Primer-Blast primer designing tool [CITATION_1] . RNA was isolated from individual testes from 5 control males and 5 males exposed to 1.2 ng/L EE 2 , homogenized in 0.8 ml/sample of TriReagent (Sigma-Aldrich, Germany) and quantified using NanoDrop ND-1000 spectrophotometer, and RNA quality was determined as the 260/280 nm absorption ratio. Reverse transcription was performed using HotStarTaq Plus Master Mix Kit (Qiagen) from 0.5 mg RNA per sample. Bio-Rad C1000 Touch Thermal cycler TM , CFX96",
